\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Now it came to pass in the \w days|strong="H3117"\w* of \w Ahasuerus|strong="H0325"\w*, (this \add is\add* \w Ahasuerus|strong="H0325"\w* which \w reigned|strong="H4427"\w*, from \w India|strong="H1912"\w* even unto \w Ethiopia|strong="H3568"\w*, \add over\add* an \w hundred|strong="H3967"\w* and \w seven|strong="H7651"\w* and \w twenty|strong="H6242"\w* \w provinces|strong="H4082"\w*:)  
