\v 3 In the \w third|strong="H7969"\w* \w year|strong="H8141"\w* of his \w reign|strong="H4427"\w*, he \w made|strong="H6213"\w* a \w feast|strong="H4960"\w* unto all his \w princes|strong="H8269"\w* and his \w servants|strong="H5650"\w*; the \w power|strong="H2428"\w* of \w Persia|strong="H6539"\w* and \w Media|strong="H4074"\w*, the \w nobles|strong="H6579"\w* and \w princes|strong="H8269"\w* of the \w provinces|strong="H4082"\w*, \add being\add* \w before|strong="H6440"\w* him:  
