\p
\v 12 ¶ And \w Mordecai|strong="H4782"\w* came \w again|strong="H7725"\w* to the \w king’s|strong="H4428"\w* \w gate|strong="H8179"\w*. But \w Haman|strong="H2001"\w* \w hasted|strong="H1765"\w* to his \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w mourning|strong="H0057"\w*, and having his \w head|strong="H7218"\w* \w covered|strong="H2645"\w*.  
